Run and test MQTT on your local machine with Mosquitto

1) Install Mosquitto (mosquitto.org) - https://mosquitto.org/download/ 

For MAC users

2) Run Mosquitto â€“ 
      brew services start mosquitto
3) Subscriber: 
      mosquitto_sub -t topic/state -h 127.0.0.1
4) Publisher: 
      mosquitto_pub -t topic/state -m '{"temperature": 12, "pressure": 11, "humidity": 10}'

All users: 
